{
  "stem": "17606.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He said, when the Polish Army surrendered, they were throwing their arms in the middle of the street.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And our boys went out-- And picked it up.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--pick them up.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But the-- the war will take six months, another half a year, maybe a year.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We'll have more to send to the [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "To Palestine.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That was an arsenal.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that but was the-- I would say the beginning of the arms collection for the revolt.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Like I said to you, time after the war there were two organizations, the Jewish fighting organization, which led by Mordechai Anielewicz, and the Jewish military organization, which was led by Paul Frankel.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I became the-- the military instructor because of my military background.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "There weren't too many officers, Jewish officers, actually.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 7 SECONDS] In Ringelblum's memoirs, he speaks about the Jewish military organization.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he says it was a smaller group, but armed to their teeth.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "The best armed group, and we proved it in the revolt.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they came.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Then it was-- we were told-- my-- my parents told me, actually.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Joe, be careful.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Don't go out, because they are gripping to-- this to-- to slap awake.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You'll be-- they-- they're taking it to-- to the park of the Polish parliament.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they're digging graves over there where they are shotting people.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They were picking people from the streets?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "From the streets.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "At random.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They-- they saw the armband.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And there, to dig the--the graves for those who they-- whom they shot the day before, the night before.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there over in that park, they were burying them.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That's what they take, the Jews.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And my father, that's not for you.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You go through enough.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Saw enough corpses already.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
